<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>LP改善ポートフォリオ | AIコピーライティング制作サンプル</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@300;400;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ink: #1a1714;
    --cream: #f8f4ee;
    --warm: #f0e9dc;
    --accent: #c8492a;
    --accent-light: #e8d5cc;
    --gold: #b8922a;
    --muted: #7a6f65;
    --border: rgba(26,23,20,0.12);
    --serif: 'DM Serif Display', 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    --sans: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(248,244,238,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 40px; height: 60px;
  }
  .nav-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .nav-tabs { display: flex; gap: 0; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
  .tab-btn {
    padding: 8px 24px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; font-family: var(--sans);
    background: none; border: none; transition: all 0.2s;
    color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .tab-btn.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); }
  .nav-badge {
    font-size: 11px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ─── HERO SECTION ─── */
  .hero-wrapper { position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .section-label {
    text-align: center; padding: 16px 0 0;
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted); font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ─── BEFORE (old LP) ─── */
  .before-section { display: none; }
  .before-section.visible { display: block; }

  .before-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a5f 0%, #0d1f3c 100%);
    color: white; text-align: center;
    padding: 80px 40px;
  }
  .before-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: #ff6b35;
    color: white; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .before-h1 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .before-sub { font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .before-cta {
    display: inline-block; background: #ff6b35;
    color: white; padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer; border: none;
  }
  .before-features {
    display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 40px;
    padding: 60px 40px; background: #f5f5f5; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .before-feature { text-align: center; max-width: 200px; }
  .before-icon { font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .before-feature h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .before-feature p { font-size: 13px; color: #666; }
  .before-price {
    text-align: center; padding: 60px 40px;
    background: white; border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }
  .before-price h2 { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .before-price-num { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; color: #1e3a5f; }
  .before-price-note { font-size: 13px; color: #999; margin-bottom: 24px; }

  /* ─── AFTER (new LP) ─── */
  .after-section { display: none; }
  .after-section.visible { display: block; }

  .after-hero {
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    background: var(--cream);
    position: relative;
  }
  .after-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 45%; height: 100%;
    background: var(--warm);
    clip-path: polygon(15% 0, 100% 0, 100% 100%, 0% 100%);
  }
  .after-hero-inner {
    max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 48px;
    position: relative; z-index: 1;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 60px; align-items: center;
  }
  .after-eyebrow {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .after-eyebrow-line { width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
  .after-eyebrow-text {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500;
  }
  .after-h1 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 44px; line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .after-h1 em { color: var(--accent); font-style: normal; }
  .after-sub {
    font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px; max-width: 380px;
  }
  .after-cta-group { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
    padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; cursor: pointer; border: none;
    font-family: var(--sans); letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .btn-link {
    font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; cursor: pointer;
    background: none; border: none; font-family: var(--sans);
  }
  .after-social-proof { margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .proof-faces { display: flex; gap: -8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .proof-face {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--cream); margin-right: -8px;
    font-size: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    background: var(--warm);
  }
  .proof-text { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; }
  .proof-text strong { color: var(--ink); }

  /* After hero visual side */
  .after-hero-visual { position: relative; }
  .hero-card {
    background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .card-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    background: var(--accent-light); color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .card-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }
  @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.4} }
  .card-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .card-role { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .card-quote { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--ink); font-style: italic; }
  .card-stars { color: var(--gold); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 12px; }
  .mini-stat {
    position: absolute; top: -16px; right: -16px;
    background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px 16px; text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }
  .mini-stat-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 28px; display: block; }
  .mini-stat-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; opacity: 0.7; }

  /* ─── COMPARISON TABLE ─── */
  .comparison { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 80px 40px; }
  .comparison-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 32px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .comparison-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 48px; font-size: 14px; }

  .insight-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 24px; }
  .insight-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 28px;
    background: white;
  }
  .insight-card.problem { border-left: 3px solid #d97b6c; }
  .insight-card.solution { border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); }
  .insight-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .insight-tag {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .problem .insight-tag { background: #fde8e4; color: #c0392b; }
  .solution .insight-tag { background: #fef3d4; color: #8b6914; }
  .insight-point { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .insight-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; }
  .insight-copy {
    margin-top: 12px; padding: 10px 14px;
    border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; font-style: italic;
  }
  .problem .insight-copy { background: #fdf0ee; color: #7a3228; }
  .solution .insight-copy { background: #fefae8; color: #5c4a10; }
  .copy-label { font-size: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; opacity: 0.6; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* ─── PROCESS ─── */
  .process-section { background: var(--ink); color: var(--cream); padding: 80px 40px; }
  .process-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .process-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .process-sub { color: rgba(248,244,238,0.6); margin-bottom: 48px; font-size: 14px; }
  .process-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
  .process-step { display: flex; gap: 32px; padding: 28px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .process-step:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 40px; color: rgba(248,244,238,0.2);
    min-width: 48px; line-height: 1;
  }
  .step-content h3 { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .step-content p { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(248,244,238,0.6); line-height: 1.7; }
  .step-tools { display: flex; gap: 8px; margin-top: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tool-pill {
    font-size: 11px; padding: 3px 10px; border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(248,244,238,0.2); color: rgba(248,244,238,0.7);
  }

  /* ─── RESULTS ─── */
  .results-section { padding: 80px 40px; max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .results-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 32px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .results-sub { text-align: center; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 48px; font-size: 14px; }
  .results-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .result-card {
    text-align: center; padding: 32px 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; background: white;
  }
  .result-num {
    font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 52px; color: var(--accent);
    line-height: 1; display: block; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .result-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }
  .result-detail { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 6px; opacity: 0.7; }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  .portfolio-footer {
    text-align: center; padding: 48px; background: var(--warm);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .footer-note { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
  .footer-title { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

  /* ─── ANNOTATION LAYER ─── */
  .annotation {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    background: var(--accent); color: white;
    font-size: 11px; padding: 4px 10px 4px 8px; border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 500; cursor: default;
    position: relative;
  }
  .annotation-num {
    width: 16px; height: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    border-radius: 50%; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .annotations-bar {
    background: #fff8f5; border: 1px solid var(--accent-light);
    border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px 24px; margin: 0 40px 0;
    display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;
  }
  .ann-item { font-size: 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; color: var(--muted); }
  .ann-num-badge {
    width: 20px; height: 20px; background: var(--accent); color: white;
    border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .divider {
    text-align: center; padding: 16px 0 0; font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }

  .big-arrow {
    text-align: center; padding: 8px 0 16px; font-size: 28px; color: var(--muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .after-hero-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .after-hero::before { display: none; }
    .insight-grid, .results-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    nav { padding: 0 20px; }
    .tab-btn { padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 12px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-logo">Portfolio</div>
  <div class="nav-tabs">
    <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="showTab('before')">Before</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('after')">After</button>
    <button class="tab-btn" onclick="showTab('analysis')">改善分析</button>
  </div>
  <span class="nav-badge">制作サンプル</span>
</nav>

<!-- ============================================================
     BEFORE TAB
============================================================ -->
<div class="before-section visible" id="tab-before">
  <div class="section-label">改善前 ／ 既存LP（架空）</div>
  <div style="height:16px;"></div>

  <!-- Before Hero -->
  <div class="before-hero">
    <span class="before-badge">🎉 期間限定キャンペーン中！</span>
    <h1 class="before-h1">オンライン英語コーチング<br>はじめてみませんか？</h1>
